						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1548 (1626 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Registers a gift of land as <hi rend="italic">tirunāmattukkāṇi</hi> to the temple. The details of the date, viz., <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1547, Kshaya, Vṛīśchika ba. 5, Monday, Pūsam</hi> correspond to <hi rend="bold">1626, A.D. November 27, Monday, f.d.t. ·11; ·24. The Śaka year quoted is wrong for 1548.</hi></p>						

